data.description: Vacant and ready for immediate occupancy. Brand new rambler construction featuring 1344+ finished sq ft on the main level and a full unfinished basement. The main floor features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths (inc. master), vaulted ceilings, Samsung appliance package and laundry. The basement has poured insulated concrete walls, 9ft ceilings, 2 egress windows and an ideal footprint for future expansion. Maintenance free siding, seamless gutters, Thermotech windows and a huge deck tie it all together. A 30x64 shop on slab with (4) overhead doors has your vehicles and toys covered. Lightning fast internet (fiber) provided through Paul Bunyan's Gigazone. Gorgeous setting on 5 pine studded acres with a 10ft deeded access to the Heartland Trail. Perfect location between Park Rapids and Nevis.
